    v2 = wp.cos((0.88 - wp.cos(v2 + 0.37)))
    v1 = 0.39
    tmp = wp.cos((0.87 + v0))
    v0 = wp.abs(((tmp + 0.83 / tmp + 0.59) * wp.exp(v2 + 0.24)))
